{
  "id": "RAW_8399d8af",
  "title": "熬死 5 家初创公司老鸟揭露业内残酷真相：70%的 Agent 产品系 OpenAI 套壳，没有上下文和工具，智能体就是笨蛋！无限记忆是陷阱",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODI5Njc2MA==&mid=2655929396&idx=1&sn=7e6c9a303b88183caef048f81ca37a9e",
  "date": "2025-10-11 05:51:00",
  "author": "51CTO技术栈",
  "siteName": "51CTO技术栈",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">编辑 | 云昭</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"75\" data-end=\"138\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">先坦白一件事：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"75\" data-end=\"138\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI Agent 不是魔法。它们脆弱、多变，更像是喝了咖啡的实习生，而不是能独立完成任务的员工。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"140\" data-end=\"236\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但我确实在 5 家初创公司里，造过 300 多个 Agent。我看过它们惊艳的成功，也看过它们惨烈的崩溃。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"140\" data-end=\"236\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我见过投资人被炫目的 Demo 迷住，然后在现实到来时拔腿就跑。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"238\" data-end=\"260\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以下，是我学到的一切——未经粉饰的版本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"508428128\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df6c4681&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvFXuhILX3JhsfmCGP3UXkY5FYq08vSDZ3iboc71BweGlL0gcgibaGG0Jw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"267\" data-end=\"292\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">没有上下文，Agent 就是笨蛋</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"294\" data-end=\"349\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大家都爱说：“Agent 是未来。”</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但说实话：一个孤立的 Agent，不过是穿着西装的鹦鹉。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"351\" data-end=\"436\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">真正决定 Agent 水平的，是</span></span><strong data-start=\"367\" data-end=\"376\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">上下文注入</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">(</span></span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">context injection</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。给它合适的记忆、数据源和语境，它就像变魔术一样聪明。缺了这些，它就会一本正经地胡说八道，立刻摧毁信任。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"438\" data-end=\"472\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">教训：Agent 的“聪明”，完全取决于你喂它的上下文。</span></span></p>\n  <pre data-start=\"474\" data-end=\"923\"><div><p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p><pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"padding:16px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span style=\"line-height:26px;font-style:italic;\"><span leaf=\"\"># Example: Context matters</span></span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">from</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;langchain.agents&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">import</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;initialize_agent, Tool</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">from</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;langchain.llms&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">import</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;OpenAI</span></code></pre><p></p></div></pre>\n  <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n  <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"padding:16px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">tools = [</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Tool(</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; name=</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"SearchDB\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; func=</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">lambda</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;q:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">f\"Fake DB results for&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">{q}</span></span><span leaf=\"\">\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">,</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; description=</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"useful for answering database questions\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; )</span><span leaf=\"\">]</span><span leaf=\"\">llm = OpenAI(temperature=</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">0</span></span><span leaf=\"\">)</span><span leaf=\"\">agent = initialize_agent(tools, llm, agent=</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"zero-shot-react-description\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">)</span><span leaf=\"\">response = agent.run(</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"What are last month’s sales?\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">)</span><span leaf=\"\">print(response)</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p data-start=\"925\" data-end=\"952\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不接入真实数据库？垃圾。连上数据仓库？黄金。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"508428129\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=65f7dc56&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVv7ibyGuL0I4icm8WDcjJED18MoII9zQibicm14LThHibzUyEx9XKLuhLcbnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"959\" data-end=\"988\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">大多数 Agent 产品只是“高价包装”</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"990\" data-end=\"1050\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">行业的“丑陋”真相是：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"990\" data-end=\"1050\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">70% 的“AI Agent 初创公司”，其实只是包了层壳的 OpenAI API</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1052\" data-end=\"1140\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">界面光鲜，PPT 高级，Demo 爆火。可一剥皮，你发现它们本质就是</span></span><code data-start=\"1092\" data-end=\"1124\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">openai.ChatCompletion.create()</span></span></code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;+ 一点 JSON 解析。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1142\" data-end=\"1186\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">教训：不要把 UI 的精致误认为创新。能让你花一个周末就能复刻的东西，没护城河。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"508428131\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d876485&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvxSHbjbhmqPxCwjQ6qqBkHI3m9IDoV0x2pqqY78zMd9eu5sA4ee0KCQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1193\" data-end=\"1223\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">多 Agent 协作听起来聪明，实际上更蠢</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1225\" data-end=\"1275\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“让多个 Agent 互相对话”听起来很炫。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我做过几十次，看起来像专家会议。结果呢？</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1277\" data-end=\"1333\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们互相兜圈。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1277\" data-end=\"1333\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们一致同意错误答案。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1277\" data-end=\"1333\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们烧 Token 的速度，比你交 OpenAI 账单还快。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1335\" data-end=\"1382\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">教训：一个设计良好的单 Agent + 工具，比十个互聊的 Agent 有用多了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"508428133\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e356694&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvlydibLicaBC57FUZw91MhHHCNmBlamtdImWmImY9u5Yzw0SlcdNLnb5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1389\" data-end=\"1410\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">记忆既是超能力，也是陷阱</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1412\" data-end=\"1499\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">创业公司都爱吹：“我们的 Agent 会记住你前 50 次对话！”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1412\" data-end=\"1499\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">没错，这很酷。但很快，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">直到记忆膨胀，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Agent 变慢，成本暴涨，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">还突然回忆起你三个月前打错的字。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1501\" data-end=\"1544\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">关键不在于“无限记忆”，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而在于</span></span><strong data-start=\"1519\" data-end=\"1528\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">策略性记忆</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">分段回忆、向量搜索、剪枝。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1546\" data-end=\"1567\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">教训：记太多和记太少一样没用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"508428132\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ac2d0dd8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvWXnSu9Q4wStccUsIJfVTNK1OfmxCNJAoXH8qTiaUtWgsiaGBo97KdhoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1574\" data-end=\"1598\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">难的是 UX，不是 Agent</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1600\" data-end=\"1648\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">直说了——</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">造 Agent 只占 10% 难度。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">让用户信任它，占 90%。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1650\" data-end=\"1707\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">清晰的 AI / 人类交接点。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1650\" data-end=\"1707\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">透明的日志，让错误不再像黑盒。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1650\" data-end=\"1707\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">防呆机制，别让一次傻回答毁掉产品口碑。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1709\" data-end=\"1741\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">教训：赢在“失败体验”的设计，不在“最聪明的模型”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"508428134\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c94ffe18&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvIlCcG9KsdSpHE4IadUmg5FP5cAszuTial2YXAI7vcltzDmiaWX99rUUg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1748\" data-end=\"1777\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">大多数 Agent 的失败是“静悄悄”的</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1779\" data-end=\"1822\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">没人愿意承认这一点：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Agent 通常不会爆炸式失败。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们是悄悄地“软刀子式”的出错。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1824\" data-end=\"1876\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">答错一点点，没人发现。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1824\" data-end=\"1876\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">生成半有用的报告，浪费你几小时。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1824\" data-end=\"1876\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">嘴上说“完成了”，其实什么都没干。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1878\" data-end=\"1927\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong data-start=\"1878\" data-end=\"1924\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">教训：</span></span><strong data-start=\"1883\" data-end=\"1917\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Agent 的可靠性，不看炫技 Demo，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">要看几个月的</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">平静正确性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"508428135\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2e9f3b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvIt3S48rlta8aYtfbHzVXh6LjLPCYqXiazwthaFlDwOqvn9tS8ezRTKw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1934\" data-end=\"1960\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">真正的价值在“工具”，不是“自治”</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1962\" data-end=\"1997\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人人都梦想“完全自主的 Agent”。现实是：自治被高估了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1999\" data-end=\"2068\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">价值点实际上在于</span></span><strong data-start=\"2003\" data-end=\"2014\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可调用的工具链</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：API、脚本、连接器。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1999\" data-end=\"2068\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当 Agent 变成任务编排者，而不是“自由思想者”，它才真正有用。</span></span></p>\n  <pre data-start=\"2070\" data-end=\"2395\"><div><p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p><pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"padding:16px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span style=\"line-height:26px;font-style:italic;\"><span leaf=\"\"># Example: Tool-driven agent &gt; fully \"autonomous\" one</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">def</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">send_email</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">(to, subject, body)</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">return</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">f\"Email sent to&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">{to}</span></span><span leaf=\"\">:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">{subject}</span></span><span leaf=\"\">\"</span></span></code></pre><p></p></div></pre>\n  <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n  <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"padding:16px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">tools = [Tool(name=</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"Email\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">, func=send_email, description=</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"Sends email\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">)]</span><span leaf=\"\">agent = initialize_agent(tools, llm, agent=</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"zero-shot-react-description\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">)</span><span leaf=\"\">print(agent.run(</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">\"Send an email to Alex saying project is approved.\"</span></span><span leaf=\"\">))</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2397\" data-end=\"2431\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">是不是有点“无聊”？这正是重点：它能</span></span><strong data-start=\"2417\" data-end=\"2428\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">每次都成功运行</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2433\" data-end=\"2458\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">教训：自治是硅谷的幻想，编排才是现实。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"508428136\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5ab07df9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvkmLrLib3UecMC2ZI7egSibib8uhdd56gd6KibxxcXegOGzVOdghMXIB9TA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"2465\" data-end=\"2480\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">市场极其残酷</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"2482\" data-end=\"2520\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我亲眼看过 5 家 Agent 创业公司兴衰。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们的死因惊人一致：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2524\" data-end=\"2549\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong data-start=\"2524\" data-end=\"2530\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">延迟</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：没人愿意等 60 秒的“魔法”。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2552\" data-end=\"2570\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong data-start=\"2552\" data-end=\"2558\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">成本</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：企业账单远超收入。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"2573\" data-end=\"2614\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><strong data-start=\"2573\" data-end=\"2581\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">炒作消退</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：投资人发现你的“Agent”其实只有 3 个 API 调用。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"2616\" data-end=\"2655\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但我也见过幸存者：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">能解决一个具体痛点，比人更快、更稳的产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2657\" data-end=\"2694\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">教训：垂直细分 + 稳定性，胜过“我们要做通用 Agent”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"508428137\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=50e7130e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvy4BTx0H2vBD5LlxZM7T7OSsyF5rH4toIC9ibiayvn1cr0dS3V0Wg254g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"2701\" data-end=\"2727\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">最好的Agent，不像Agent</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"2729\" data-end=\"2769\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">300 次构建后，我得出结论：未来不是“每个人都有个 Jarvis”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2771\" data-end=\"2789\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而是</span></span><strong data-start=\"2773\" data-end=\"2786\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">隐形的 Agent</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2791\" data-end=\"2855\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们深度嵌入工作流，你甚至感觉不到它们的存在。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2791\" data-end=\"2855\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不再是花哨的聊天机器人，而是默默节省你时间的“无声操作员”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2857\" data-end=\"2887\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就像自动补全那样。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2857\" data-end=\"2887\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就像邮件在你思考前就起草好那样。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2889\" data-end=\"2929\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">教训：最好的 Agent，不像 Agent。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它们让生活更顺滑。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2936\" data-end=\"2988\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我造了 300 个 Agent。大多数失败了，少数成功了。但它们都教会我同一个残酷事实：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"2992\" data-end=\"3038\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI Agent 没有什么所谓的魔法，它们只是工具。</span></span></p>\n   <p data-start=\"2992\" data-end=\"3038\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而所有工具的价值，取决于使用它的人。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"3040\" data-end=\"3105\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以真正的问题并非：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“Agent 什么时候会更聪明？”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"3040\" data-end=\"3105\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而是：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">“我们什么时候能更聪明地使用它们？”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"3040\" data-end=\"3105\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">好了，接下来麦克风交给评论区的各位大佬：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"3040\" data-end=\"3105\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">我们是在迎来“Agent 革命”，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">还是又一个即将烧光的炒作周期？</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "资深从业者揭露 AI Agent 开发中的残酷真相，强调上下文、工具链和用户体验的重要性，并警示过度炒作和“套壳”现象。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "资深从业者揭露 AI Agent 开发中的残酷真相，强调上下文、工具链和用户体验的重要性，并警示过度炒作和“套壳”现象。",
  "summary": "文章基于作者在五家初创公司构建 300 多个 AI Agent 的经验，对当前 AI Agent 领域的过度炒作和不切实际的期望进行了深刻反思，并深入剖析了产品开发中的多项“残酷真相”。作者指出，Agent 的智能程度并非源于模型本身，而是完全取决于上下文注入的质量。他揭示了行业中 70%的 Agent 初创公司仅仅是对 OpenAI API 的“高价包装”，缺乏核心技术壁垒。同时，文章批判了多 Agent 协作的低效与高成本，以及“无限记忆”的陷阱，强调策略性记忆的重要性。作者进一步指出，Agent 开发的真正难点在于用户体验设计和“失败体验”管理，而非 Agent 本身。文章总结认为 Agent 的真正价值在于作为任务编排者调用工具链，而非追求完全自治，并预言未来的 Agent 将是深度嵌入工作流的“隐形操作员”。文章最终强调，AI Agent 并非魔法，而是工具，其价值取决于人类如何更聪明地使用它们，而非沉迷于炒作。",
